import { Button, Card, CardActionArea, CardActions, CardContent, CardMedia, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import React from 'react'

export const Feed = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 400, marginTop:"200px" ,marginLeft:"30px"}} >
        <Grid
          container
          direction="row"
          justifyContent="space-around"
          alignItems="flex-start">

        </Grid>
        <CardActionArea>
          <CardMedia
            component="img"
            height="200"
            image="https://cdn.dsmcdn.com/ty864/pimWidgetApi/mobile_20230504173320_2316859ElektronikMobile202305042001.jpg"
            alt="teknosa"
          />
          <CardContent>
            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
              teknosa
            </Typography>

          </CardContent>
        </CardActionArea>
        <CardActions>
          <Button
            size='small'
            color='inherit'
          >
            alışverişe başla
          </Button>
        </CardActions>
        <CardActionArea>
          <CardMedia
            component="img"
            height="200"
            image="https://cdn.dsmcdn.com/ty870/pimWidgetApi/mobile_20230507171702_2311009KadinMobile202305042001.jpg"
            alt="mango"
          />
          <CardContent>
            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
              mango
            </Typography>

          </CardContent>
        </CardActionArea>
        <CardActions>
          <Button
            size='small'
            color='inherit'
          >
            alışverişe başla
          </Button>
        </CardActions>
        <CardActionArea>
          <CardMedia
            component="img"
            height="200"
            image="https://cdn.dsmcdn.com/ty849/pimWidgetApi/mobile_20230428123101_2303698KadinMobile202304251501.jpg"
            alt="skechers"
          />
          <CardContent>
            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
              skechers
            </Typography>

          </CardContent>
        </CardActionArea>
        <CardActions>
          <Button
            size='small'
            color='inherit'
          >
            alışverişe başla
          </Button>
        </CardActions>


      </Card> 
       </>   
  )}
